long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Job application tracker. an open-source solution designed to streamline your job search. This tool allows you to effortlessly save relevant information directly to your private Google Sheets, providing an organized and secure way to manage your applications.

Key features include:

* Seamless Integration: With a single click, capture company and position details from job posting, making application tracking hassle-free.
* Enhanced Experience: Instantly spot which job postings you've applied to with easily recognizable applied badges.
* Efficient Quick Search: Find specific applications swiftly and efficiently.
* Supported Websites: Linkedin, Glassdoor 

Moreover, this project serves as an excellent starting point for your next TypeScript React Chrome extension. Feel free to explore, adapt, and contribute by forking the repository: https://github.com/Jianxuan-Li/junt. Your feedback and contributions are highly appreciated.
